Known Bugs
-------------

- dbus.exceptions.DBusException: tr.org.pardus.comar.Comar.PolicyKit: tr.org.pardus.comar.net.link.getauth
    Click 'Edit' for a Wireless profile. PolicyKit will ask you to enter your password to show the profile
    details. Click 'Cancel'. You'll get that exception and the Edit button will stay clicked, UI is broken.
- Available Profiles is added per backend/device, this should be fixed.
